headline.main: Koenig Hits 5 3s on Senior Day, No. 22 Badgers Beats Gophers
headline.print_headline: Koenig Hits 5 3s on Senior Day, No. 22 Badgers Beats Gophers

lead_paragraph: Bronson Koenig had a disappointing start to his final home game at Wisconsin, spending most of the first half watching from the bench because of foul trouble.
